  • Method Details

    • receiveMove

      public void receiveMove(RowColPair pair)
      Receives the move provided by a TimeLimitedSimulatedPlayer. The player can provide multiple moves in response to a single call to TimeLimitedSimulatedPlayer.makeMove(GameModel, TileColor, Listener) The last one before time runs out will be played.
      Parameters:
      pair - the board position of the move
